\v 14 ∆ó king Erod\f + \fr 6:14 \ft D…®k…®nd king Erod re Erod Antipate yete re ukoyam king Erod…®mna b'…®ga. Ton ti b'u…®m p…®lke akatonj Galili eriya d…®de Peraya eriya w…®p iyoy…®m.\f* daka kea y…®d…®r y…®t utkundonj Yesum gatab. Mop nok…®p Yesu ma ny…® re kea p…®tak…®p…®nd awonj d…®de r…®gap Yesum gatab b'engabenga w…®p ke y…®t apurento. S…® n…®nda r…®gap yopureno da, ‚ÄúBaptiso Yoan kea uj ke utnyitonj. S…® ongg…®t mop paemb Yoan…®mna k…®d kesa k…®ma dandate w…®ko omn…®ka yiyeny …®temb r…®ga Yesum p…®l…®nd.‚Äù  
