\v 17-18 S…® …®temb j…® y…®t r…®ja na re Erod Baptiso Yoan…®nd mop y…®pendonj. S…® re king Erod ti y…®nggan Pilip…®mna kongga Erodiyand wokatonj ti konggam, s…® Yoan king Erod…®nd yomnenonj da, ‚Äú∆ótemb re ma b'og…®l m…®le emb j…®, man …®tomb mor y…®nggan…®m kongga mor konggam womny…®t.‚Äù S…® ongg…®t penaemb ket king Erod Yoan…®nd y…®m…®nd yusunatonj d…®de y…®job…®konj …® ket s…®b…®bmet wa yoramitonj ti kongga Erodiyand nony b'og…®l omnam.  
\v 19 Aj…® Erodiya re ma sobijog na Yoan…®m p…®lwa soro aukenenonj, ng…®rpu singi awonj tin ongandam. Aj…® ma r…®r…®r na awonj.  
