\v 26 Seg, king Erod ma sobijog na gar beb…®g awonj, aj…® ton ma r…®r…®r na awonj ng…®mngai ma b'arkita b'…®sayam, nok…®p ton kea God ma ny…® k…®ma okawam womnonj komkesa …®ngauki r…®ga wa w…®p…®nd.  
\v 27 S…® odenja king Erod ara yemokonj y…®pa tina y…®r …®pka geja r…®ga, …® yingawonj Yoan…®mna moptek…®p iyoy…®m. Re ket geja r…®ga yiwatonj s…®b…®bmet wa, ton kea ket Yoan…®nd mop y…®pendonj.  
